info</a>
</p>
<p>
<a href="http://www.fs.fed.us/r5/shastatrinity/index.shtml">Shasta-Trinity National
Forest</a><br>
<a href="http://www.fs.fed.us/r5/shastatrinity/documents/st-main/maps/rogs/mccloud/upr-mc-r.pdf">Upper
McCloud River Area</a> pdf (155 Kb) McCloud Loop brochure<br>
<a href="http://www.fs.fed.us/r5/shastatrinity/documents/st-main/maps/rogs/mccloud/mc-rec.pdf">McCloud
Area Recreation Guide</a> pdf (203 Kb)
</p>
<p>
&nbsp;
</p>
<p>
Wyntoon information:<br>
